languages.text: "Ничто не поможет. Только время сотрет боль из памяти, оставив зажившие шрамы души и тела. Однако ты получил{mf||а} бесценный опыт, элантах. Дата отпор Темным и победил{mf||а}. Это более чем достойное разрешение случившегося".

"Nothing will help. Only time can erase the pain from memory, leaving healed scars on body and mind. But you have gained some invaluable experience, elantach. You have resisted the Drukhari and emerged victorious. This is a more than worthy outcome."

languages.text: “没有任何事情能挽回失落的一切，只有时间能够抹去记忆的伤痛，在身体和心灵上留下愈合的伤痕。不过，外界人，你挡住了黑暗灵族的进攻，取得了胜利。这是宝贵的经验，也是值得骄傲的战果。”

languages.text: «Nada lo hará. Únicamente el tiempo borrará el dolor de su recuerdo, dejando sus cicatrices en cuerpo y mente. Pero has adquirido una experiencia que no tiene precio, elantach. Te has enfrentado a los Drukhari y has salido {mf|victorioso|victoriosa}. Es un desenlace más que digno».
languages.original_text: "Nothing will help. Only time can erase the pain from memory, leaving healed scars on body and mind. But you have gained some invaluable experience, elantach. You have resisted the Drukhari and emerged victorious. This is a more than worthy outcome."

languages.text: « C'est vrai. Seul le temps pourra effacer la douleur des souvenirs, qui laissera derrière elle des cicatrices sur votre corps et votre esprit. Mais vous avez gagné une expérience précieuse, elantach. Vous avez résisté aux Drukharis et remporté la victoire. C'est déjà un exploit. »
languages.original_text: "Nothing will help. Only time can erase the pain from memory, leaving healed scars on body and mind. But you have gained some invaluable experience, elantach. You have resisted the Drukhari and emerged victorious. This is a more than worthy outcome."

languages.text: "Nichts wird helfen. Nur die Zeit kann den Schmerz aus dem Gedächtnis tilgen und verheilte Narben auf Körper und Geist zurücklassen. Aber Ihr habt eine unschätzbar wertvolle Erfahrung gemacht, Elantach. Ihr habt den Drukhari widerstanden und seid siegreich daraus hervorgegangen. Das ist ein mehr als würdiges Resultat."
languages.original_text: "Nothing will help. Only time can erase the pain from memory, leaving healed scars on body and mind. But you have gained some invaluable experience, elantach. You have resisted the Drukhari and emerged victorious. This is a more than worthy outcome."

languages.text: "Hiçbir şey getirmeyecek. Hatıralardaki yaraları yalnızca zaman silebilir ama o da bedeninde ve zihninde iyileşmiş yara izleri bırakır. Sen paha biçilemez deneyimler kazandın elantach. Drukharilere karşı gelip zafere ulaştın. Oldukça değerli bir sonuç bu."
